ygData.subject: Re: Best 1h blunt weapon...
ygData.msgSnippet: shes around level 42 and you can only get to her with an experienced group that knows that castle well.. .ive heard a group of high 45ths-50ths were wiped out
ygData.messageBody:
shes around level 42 and you can only get to her with an experienced group
that knows that castle well.. .ive heard a group of high 45ths-50ths were
wiped out in less then 45min after going for it.. but I knew a druid 50th
level that could get the princess out of the castle and solo her (since
druids in wolf form are not aggro'd until their faction gets really low in
there).

So it depends.. its a very rare dropped item.... shes 42nd and I have no
idea how often she spawns.
